a/majemoji\">majemoji</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/metalogica/majemoji\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">1</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":1,\"repo\":\"metalogica/majemoji\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - Adds a random emoji to each session's prompt. Includes <code>git</code> status decorations.</li>","updatedAt":"2022-05-23T15:02:17.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"paragonie/awesome-appsec","categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://securingthestack.com\">Securing The Stack</a></h3>\n<p>Bi-Weekly Appsec Tutorials</p>","updatedAt":"2022-05-23T05:21:58.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"paragonie/awesome-appsec","categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://www.owasp.org/index.php/OWASP_Serverless_Goat\">OWASP ServerlessGoat</a></h3>\n<p>OWASP ServerlessGoat is a deliberately insecure realistic AWS Lambda serverless application, maintained by OWASP and created by <a href=\"https://www.puresec.io/\">PureSec</a>. You can install WebGoat, learn about the vulnerabilities, how to exploit them, and how to remediate each issue. The project also includes documentation explaining the issues and how they should be remediated with best-practices.</p>","updatedAt":"2022-05-23T05:21:58.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"paragonie/awesome-appsec","categoryHTML":"<h2>Websites</h2>","itemHTML":"<h4><a href=\"https://clickjacker.io\">clickjacker.io</a></h4>\n<p>Test and learn Clickjacking. Make clickjacking PoC, take screenshot and share link. You can test HTTPS, HTTP, intranet &#x26; internal sites.</p>","updatedAt":"2022-05-23T05:21:58.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"paragonie/awesome-appsec","categoryHTML":"<h2>Tools</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://www.puresec.io/function-shield\">PureSec FunctionShield</a></h3>\n<p>FunctionShield is a 100% free AWS Lambda security and Google Cloud Functions security library that equips developers with the ability to easily enforce strict security controls on serverless runtimes.</p>","updatedAt":"2022-05-23T05:21:58.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"paragonie/awesome-appsec","categoryHTML":"<h2>Books and ebooks</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://docs.fedoraproject.org/en-US/Fedora_Security_Team/1/html/Defensive_Coding/index.html\">Defensive Coding: A Guide to Improving Software Security by the Fedora Security Team</a> (2022)</h3>\n<p><strong>Released</strong>: May 23, 2022</p>\n<p>Provides guidelines for improving software security through secure coding. Covers common programming languages and libraries, and focuses on concrete recommendations.</p>","updatedAt":"2022-05-23T05:21:58.000Z"},{"awesomeListRepo":"paragonie/awesome-appsec","categoryHTML":"<h2>Repositories</h2>","itemHTML":"<h3><a href=\"https://github.com/nubank/clj-owasp\">Clojure OWASP</a><a data-role=\"trackawesomelist-badge\" href=\"https://github.com/nubank/clj-owasp\" style=\"text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;\"><span style=\"padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;\">stars</span><span style=\"padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;\">18</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{\"type\":\"repo\",\"stargazerCount\":18,\"repo\":\"nubank/clj-owasp\"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> (2020)</h3